            <h2>WE ARE HERE FOR YOU</h2>
            <p>TopHill Insurance plc is a composite Insurance company licensed to transact Life and Non-Life Insurance business in Nigeria, delivering a range of retail products such as Motor, Life,Home Insurance and corporate products to more than 30,000 customers..</p>

            <p>Incorporated in 2000 as Assurance Company plc, the company was relaunched as <strong>Ensure Insurance</strong> plc in 2016. It was acquired in 2018 by TopHill and rebranded as TopHill Nigeria Insurance plc. In 2020, the company generated gross written premiums of <i>N7.67billion</i> representing an 86% growth over 2016 <i>(N4.19billion)</i>.
            </p>
        </section>

